RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT CLASS_CODE FROM LFTMS_ACCR_FEE_CLASS WHERE MODULE = ?

SELECT CLASS_CODE, CLASS_DESCRIPTION FROM (SELECT A.CLASS_CODE, A.CLASS_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_CLASS A, LFTMS_ACCR_FEE_CLASS B WHERE A.MODULE = ? AND A.CLASS_TYPE = 'AF' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.ONCE_AUTH ='Y' AND A.CLASS_CODE = B.CLASS_CODE AND A.MODULE = B.MODULE) WHERE 1=1
